Learning Environment
--------------------
We have created a VirtualBox Appliance to use for our training.  The stock install is as follows:
 
Scientific Linux version 6.1  <-- no Gnome 3 for us,  ;-) 
git
subversion
cvs
mercurial
openjdk-devel
bzr
Eclipse Helios 3.6
JBoss Tools
M2E
eGit
SubClipse
Maven
Ant
JBoss AS 5.1.0
